            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "When a dark cult abducts his sibling, there’s nothing else Killian can do but to comply with their demands. In order to save his sister he travels to the mysterious island of Esha - a place forgotten by even gods themselves, where an unspeakable ritual is about to take place. ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 2,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Theatre Of Sorrows",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": " is a Lovecraftian-inspired roguelite where it’s up to Killian to journey through Esha and dive into dark secrets of its inhabitants; lead Killian through the unknown with only a handful of hints that might lead him to a dangerous discovery about things that should have been consigned to oblivion.",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
        "direction": "ltr",
        "format": "",
        "indent": 0,
        "type": "paragraph",
        "version": 1
