            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "’ art style perfectly conveys the creepy unsettling feeling that comes with the island of Esha. While Killian’s depiction is of a clean and well presented man, everything around him is dark and dirty, portrayed beautifully with a very manic, scratchy shading style.",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
