        "version": 1
      },
      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "The game divides its gameplay nicely into small bite-sized pieces. Each main objective can be completed within 10-15 minutes, giving it that “just one more run” feeling that roguelites thrive on.",
